              <section>

                  
          <div data-content-element-selector="p, .js-buylink-item-container" data-allowed-classes-selector="js-buylink-item-container">
                <p>Death Stranding 2: On the Beach preorders are starting to go live at major retailers, but big fans of Hideo Kojima will want to move fast to secure the Collector's Edition. Exclusive to PlayStation Direct, <a href="https://clicks.trx-hub.com/xid/fandom_32094_gamespot?q=https%3A%2F%2Fgo.skimresources.com%2F%3Fid%3D225336X1707200%26xs%3D1%26xcust%3Dsubid_value%26url%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fdirect.playstation.com%2Fen-us%2Fbuy-games%2Fdeath-stranding-2-on-the-beach-collectors-edition-ps5&amp;p=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.gamespot.com%2Farticles%2Fdeath-stranding-2-collectors-edition-preorders-are-available-now%2F1100-6530003%2F%3Fftag%3DCAD-01-10abi2f&amp;event_type=click" data-target="true" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">Death Stranding 2: On the Beach's Collector's Edition</a> is available to preorder now in limited quantities.</p><h2>Death Stranding 2 Preorder Bonuses</h2><figure data-align="center" data-size="large" data-img-src="https://www.gamespot.com/a/uploads/original/1702/17023653/4456616-39b76949d94b8c18a90f34664c1ff989%281%29.jpg" data-ref-id="1300-4456616" data-ratio="0.563" data-width="1000" data-embed-type="image"><a href="https://www.gamespot.com/a/uploads/original/1702/17023653/4456616-39b76949d94b8c18a90f34664c1ff989%281%29.jpg" data-ref-id="1300-4456616"></a><figcaption>Death Stranding 2 Preorder Bonuses</figcaption><img src="https://www.gamespot.com/a/uploads/original/1702/17023653/4456616-39b76949d94b8c18a90f34664c1ff989%281%29.jpg"></figure><p>Pick up any version of Death Stranding to get the following in-game bonuses:</p><ul><li>Quokka Hologram</li><li>Battle Skeleton: Silver (LV1, LV2, LV3)</li><li>Boost Skeleton: Silver (LV1, LV2, LV3)</li><li>Bokka Skeleton: Silver (LV1, LV2, LV3)</li></ul><p>Along with these bonuses, the Death Stranding 2 Digital Deluxe and Collector's Editions will also include up to 48-hour early access to the full game starting June 24.</p><div title="6530003 - Death Stranding 2 Preorders" data-embed-type="buylink