randing 2 gets you the base game and any eligible preorder bonuses, making it the most affordable way to get your hands on Hideo Kojima’s latest creation. Preorders will be available at all major retailers and the PlayStation Store.</p></div>                      </div>                                                                     <div>             <h2>                    <a href="https://store.playstation.com/en-us/concept/10001538" rel="sponsored nofollow" target="_blank" data-event-tracking="{&quot;destUrl&quot;:&quot;https:\/\/store.playstation.com\/en-us\/concept\/10001538&quot;,&quot;dwLinkTag&quot;:&quot;listicle|button&quot;,&quot;leadType&quot;:&quot;deal&quot;,&quot;linkLocation&quot;:&quot;BuyButton&quot;,&quot;merchantName&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;seamlessScrollPage&quot;:&quot;1&quot;,&quot;searchDim&quot;:&quot;listicle|button&quot;}" data-track-page-event="{&quot;eventName&quot;:&quot;Monetization Link Clicked&quot;,&quot;merchantName&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;merchantPrice&quot;:&quot;&quot;}" data-vars-buy-link="https://store.playstation.com/en-us/concept/10001538">Death Stranding 2: On the Beach Digital Deluxe Edition</a>       </h2>                                   <h3>                      <a href="https://store.playstation.com/en-us/concept/10001538" rel="sponsored nofollow" target="_blank" data-event-tracking="{&quot;destUrl&quot;:&quot;https:\/\/store.playstation.com\/en-us\/concept\/10001538&quot;,&quot;dwLinkTag&quot;:&quot;listicle|button&quot;,&quot;leadType&quot;:&quot;deal&quot;,&quot;linkLocation&quot;:&quot;BuyButton&quot;,&quot;merchantName&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;seamlessScrollPage&quot;:&quot;1&quot;,&quot;searchDim&quot;:&quot;listicle|button&quot;}" data-track-page-event="{&quot;eventName&quot;:&quot;Monetization Link Clicked&quot;,&quot;merchantName&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;merchantPrice&quot;:&quot;&quot;}" data-vars-buy-link="https://store.playstation.com/en-us/concept/10001538">$80</a>         </h3>                                                                                                                      <div><p>Aside from tons of in-game goodies, the big reason to pick up the Digital Deluxe Edition is for 48-hour early access to Death Stranding. So if you’re looking to dive into the action as soon as possible, it might be worth the extra $10. Along with your preorder bonuses, here’s what the Digital Deluxe Edition includes:</p><ul><li>Full game</li><li>48-hour early access to the game</li><li>Machine Gun (MP Bullets) LV1 early unlock</li><li>Battle Skeleton: Gold (LV1, LV2, LV3)</li><li>Boost Skeleton: Gold (LV1, LV2, LV3)</li><li>Bokka Skeleton: Gold (LV1, LV2, LV3)</li><li>Quokka Patch</li><li>Chiral Feline Patch</li><li>Why Me? Patch</li></ul></div>                      </div>                                                                     <div>             <h2>                    <a href="https://go.skimresources.com/?id=225336X1707200&amp;xs=1&amp;xcust=subid_value&amp;url=https://direct.playstation.com/en-us/buy-games/death-stranding-2-on-the-beach-collectors-edition-ps5" rel="sponsored nofollow" target="_blank" data-event-tracking="{&quot;destUrl&quot;:&quot;https:\/\/go.skimresources.com?id=225336X1707200&amp;xs=1&amp;xcust=subid_value&amp;url=https:\/\/direct.playstation.com\/en-us\/buy-games\/death-stranding-2-on-the-beach-collectors-edition-ps5&quot;,&quot;dwLinkTag&quot;:&quot;listicle|button&quot;,&quot;leadType&quot;:&quot;deal&quot;,&quot;linkLocation&quot;:&quot;BuyButton&quot;,&quot;merchantName&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;seamlessScrollPage&quot;:&quot;1&quot;,&quot;searchDim&quot;:&quot;listicle|button&quot;}" data-track-page-event="{&quot;eventName&quot;:&quot;Monetization Link Clicked&quot;,&quot;merchantName&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;merchantPrice&quot;:&quot;&quot;}" data-vars-buy-link="https://go.skimresources.com?id=225336X1707200&amp;xs=1&amp;xcust=subid_value&amp;url=https://direct.playstation.com/en-us/buy-games/death-stranding-2-on-the-beach-collectors-edition-ps5">Death Stranding 2: On the Beach Collector’s Edition</a>       </h2>                                   <h3>                      <a href="https://go.skimresources.com/?id=225336X1707200&amp;xs=1&amp;xcust=subid_value&amp;url=https://direct.playstation.com/en-us/buy-games/death-stranding-2-on-the-beach-collectors-edition-ps5" rel="sponsored nofollow" target="_blank" data-event-tracking="{&quot;destUrl&quot;:&quot;https:\/\/go.skimresources.com?id=225336X1707200&amp;xs=1&amp;xcust=subid_value&amp;url=https:\/\/direct.playstation.com\/en-us\/buy-games\/death-stranding-2-on-the-beach-collectors-edition-ps5&quot;,&quot;dwLinkTag&quot;:&quot;listicle|button&quot;,&quot;leadType&quot;:&quot;deal&quot;,&quot;linkLocation&quot;:&quot;BuyButton&quot;,&quot;merchantName&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;seamlessScrollPage&quot;:&quot;1&quot;,&quot;searchDim&quot;:&quot;listicle|button&quot;}" data-track-page-event="{&quot;eventName&quot;:&quot;Monetization Link Clicked&quot;,&quot;merchantName&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;merchantPrice&quot;:&quot;&quot;}" data-vars-buy-link="https://go.skimresources.com?id=225336X1707200&amp;xs=1&amp;xcust=subid_value&amp;url=https://direct.playstation.com/en-us/buy-games/death-stranding-2-on-the-beach-collectors-edition-ps5">$230</a>         </h3>                                                                                                                      <div><p>Step up to the premium Collector’s Edition to get all the digital content from the Digital Deluxe Edition, plus a bundle of physical collectibles. The highlight is a 15-inch Magellan Man Statue, though you’ll also find a collector’s box, art cards, and Dollman figurine. Here’s a full look inside:</p><ul><li>Full game</li><li>48-hour early access to the game</li><li>Collector’s box</li><li>15” Magellan Man Statue</li><li>3” Dollman figurine</li><li>Art cards</li><li>Letter from Hideo Kojima</li><li>Digital Deluxe Edition in-game items</li><li>Any eligible preorder bonuses</li></ul><p>This version has limited quantities and is exclusive to PlayStation Direct. Preorders opened in the US on March 17 at 10 AM ET.</p></div>                      </div>   </div><figure data-align="center" data-size="large" data-img-src="https://www.gamespot.com/a/uploads/original/1702/17023653/4456617-6ef059d41aa462974849a9ac0c33cc55%281%29.jpg" data-ref-id="1300-4456617" data-ratio="0.563" data-width="1000" data-embed-type="image"><a href="https://www.gamespot.com/a/uploads/original/1702/17023653/4456617-6ef059d41aa462974849a9ac0c33cc55%281%29.jpg" data-ref-id="1300-4456617"></a><figcaption>Death Stranding 2 Collector's Edition</figcaption><img src="https://www.gamespot.com/a/uploads/original/1702/17023653/4456617-6ef059d41aa462974849a9ac0c33cc55%281%29.jpg"></figure><div data-embed-type="pinbox" data-ref-id="4304">  <ul>                              <li><a href="https://www.gamespot.com/articles/playstation-pc-games-are-over-50-off-at-fanatical-cheaper-than-steam-spring-sale/1100-6530147/">PlayStation PC Games Are Over 50% Off At Fanatical, Cheaper Than Steam Spring Sale</a></li>                         <li><a href="https://www.gamespot.com/articles/the-hobbit-the-silmarillion-tolkien-illustrated-special-editions-get-100-plus-discounts/1100-6530145/">The Hobbit &amp; The Silmarillion Tolkien Illustrated Special Editions Get $100-Plus Discounts</a></li>                         <li><a href="https://www.gamespot.com/articles/the-boy-and-the-heron-steelbook-studio-ghiblis-only-4k-blu-ray-on-sale-for-best-ever-price/1100-6523029/">The Boy And The Heron Steelbook: Studio Ghibli's Only 4K Blu-Ray On Sale For Best-Ever Price</a></li>                          <li>         <span>+ Show More More Gaming, Tech, and Entertainment Deals &amp; Preorders Links (5)</span>       </li>          <li><a href="https://www.gamespot.com/articles/stephen-kings-the-stand-hardcover-edition-drops-to-lowest-price-in-years/1100-6530110/">Stephen King's The Stand Hardcover Editi